_sText:
Its more than classic jail map, because it was made to be simple but funny. And it is! You know how to play Jail mod so you dont need to explain anything.
Contains:
- 24 T spawns
- 21 CT spawns
- Random cell with a pistol (6 options)
- Random cell with a vent (2 options)
- Tic Tac Toe 5x5
- RACE 1vs1 (loser can be killed or released)
- Basketball
- Soccer/Football
- Climb
- Swimming Pool with Minigame
- Rope jump
- Bomb Toss
- Spray Contest Wall
- Others you have to discover yourself :)
